dct_title_s: Sketch map of Mt. Kilima-Njaro by Mr. H. H. Johnston
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Routes of expedition and collecting stations shown in red. Areas of virgin forest shown in green. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 7 (1885), no. 3, pp. 137-60; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
